# CAVEATS

The format of the _.footprint_ file is produced by *pkginfo*(1) using
the *-f* option.
Differences between systems or *pkginfo* versions can cause
mismatches.
; *pkgmk*(8) performs only a line-by-line comparison and may not
; handle complex format variations.

